platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: Be a vet and heal the animals

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 與小狐狸一同治療動物夥伴
小狐狸展醫術 治療動物夥伴

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Fox and Sheep’s endearing app gives kids the power to heal—and helps parents encourage kindness and curiosity. Through trial and error, little ones figure out how to treat a sniffly owl, a sunburned rabbit, and other beautifully animated patients. Sometimes they need bandages and medicine; sometimes a healthy snack will do the trick. Animals’ flashbacks and reactions offer important clues in the delightful quest to make them smile again.
